  <section class="bg-primary section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading">The Los Angeles Institute of Architecture and Design (LAIAD)</h2>
          <hr class="light">
          <p class="text-faded">The Los Angeles Institute of Architecture and Design (LAIAD) was founded in 2001 to provide an alternative way for students to begin their architecture or design educational process.  The LAIAD mission is to provide an unsurpassed and affordable education for a small group of talented and motivated students who will be prepared to excel at the schools to which they transfer. 
            We are proud to partner with LAIAD to give international high school and college students an opportunity to building a strong project put in their portfolio. You will also develop and enhance your artistic and creative skills with prominent instructors in LAIAD. For students applying to the undergraduate and graduate architecture program, a quality portfolio is essential for admission. Summer portfolio workshop at LAIAD is an intensive and immersive four weeks hands-on architecture design program.
          </p>
          <a href="#services" id="apply" class="btn btn-default">Apply!</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

